WITH LatestHandles AS (
            SELECT did, handle
            FROM handles
            WHERE (did, created_at) IN (
                SELECT did, MAX(created_at) AS max_created_at
                FROM handles
                GROUP BY did
            )
        )
        SELECT a.did, a.email, a.password, h.handle
        FROM accounts a
        LEFT JOIN LatestHandles h ON a.did = h.did
        WHERE h.handle = ?
